In Python services,

- Always use `uv run` instead of `python3` or `pytest`.
- You can run scripts with `uv run python -m scripts.module_name`.
- You can run the unit tests with `uv run pytest`.
- You can run ruff with `uv run ruff check`.

In webapp,

- Always use `bun` instead of `npm` and `bunx` instead of `npx`.
- You can run the type-checker with `bun run check`.
- You can run the unit tests with `bun run test:run`.
- You can run eslint with `bun run lint`.
